### 1. Create Category
POST http://localhost:8081/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "Electronics"}

### 2. Create Product
POST http://localhost:8081/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "iPhone 15", "price": 999.99, "stockQuantity": 10, "categoryId": 1}

### 3. Create Customer
POST http://localhost:8081/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "Ahmed Ali", "email": "ahmed@example.com"}

### 4. Create Order via Customer
POST http://localhost:8081/api/customers/1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 5. Add Item to Order
POST http://localhost:8081/api/orders/1/items
Content-Type: application/json

{"productId": 1, "quantity": 3}

### 6. Confirm Order - Stock reduces here
POST http://localhost:8081/api/orders/1/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 7. Get Order Total
GET http://localhost:8081/api/orders/1

### 8. Update Status to SHIPPED
POST http://localhost:8081/api/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "SHIPPED"}

### 9. Update Status to DELIVERED
POST http://localhost:8081/api/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "DELIVERED"}

### 10. Cancel Order - Stock restores
POST http://localhost:8081/api/orders/2/status
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "CANCELLED"}

### 11. Delete Item from DRAFT Order
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/orders/2/items/1

### 12. Low Stock Report
GET http://localhost:8081/api/products/low-stock?threshold=10

### 13. Adjust Stock Manually
POST http://localhost:8081/api/products/1/stock-adjustment
Content-Type: application/json

{"amount": 5}

### 14. ERROR TEST - Category not found
POST http://localhost:8081/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "Test", "price": 100.0, "stockQuantity": 5, "categoryId": 999}

### 15. ERROR TEST - Insufficient Stock
POST http://localhost:8081/api/orders/2/items
Content-Type: application/json

{"productId": 1, "quantity": 999}